{"tid":1531673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想下下都跳閘就入黎！！","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T15:52:38.000Z","uid":208081,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ca741fbd7539090ba2fa8ba31ed65034dff956","tid":1531673,"uid":208081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"試過chok入到車飛既閘 有藍色貼紙個啲 佢碌棍一摸上手係粗好多 同埋個表面係好諧  一埋去準備chok落去就彈翻轉頭 好撚尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n    反而無藍色貼紙無得入車飛個啲就易好多 個啲碌棍表面係滑 手擺係棍頭用力向下chok 唔好太快放手因為一放會彈翻上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絕對唔係水平線推 記得係向下chok！ 經驗尚少 有錯請指出 多自己人就跳佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(自己區個閘玩到鬆曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"ca38de15b8c5480a19e8da4b032230f9536a3747","tid":1531673,"uid":208081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be9d233731fbf287ed802f2721b074cb1c2f1287","tid":1531673,"uid":208081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d112f9815e2d5c940549bda69222dcccd8dc3e7","tid":1531673,"uid":208081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:54:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b69d00d2dd3ef191275f5fa5dbf49906a037d4e5","tid":1531673,"uid":256632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"【持續更新】香港人九月日程表<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kEaguAX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kEaguAX</a>"},{"pid":"1916e114b6762174e6c38abf3e95c94e2f8e7458","tid":1531673,"uid":208081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:54:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e34c35521726291380b5978ab171f68f814c0c5","tid":1531673,"uid":208081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e308e7ce6195476e48cbe7d541deb307f4dc1a87","tid":